62
00:27:43,995 --> 00:27:45,038
That is that.

63
00:28:27,330 --> 00:28:27,372
.

64
00:28:28,540 --> 00:28:29,958
Whenever I could,

65
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:32,293
I went my way.

66
00:28:34,421 --> 00:28:36,464
It led from my desk

67
00:28:37,090 --> 00:28:38,591
through the village,

68
00:28:39,217 --> 00:28:40,719
on convoluted paths

69
00:28:41,344 --> 00:28:42,679
and far meadows

70
00:28:42,721 --> 00:28:44,806
on to a hidden place.

71
00:28:47,183 --> 00:28:51,229
Every evening this travel was possible

72
00:28:51,896 --> 00:28:54,899
turned the day into a successful one.

73
00:28:56,484 --> 00:29:00,071
I knew that no one
would cross my paths there

74
00:29:00,071 --> 00:29:02,115
and that I could feel at home.

75
00:29:04,284 --> 00:29:05,493
Alone I was,

76
00:29:05,869 --> 00:29:09,622
gazing in amazement
at the magnitude of the setting sun –

77
00:29:10,415 --> 00:29:15,253
yet feeling in company
with the greatest men in history.

78
00:29:16,504 --> 00:29:18,423
Nothing could be compared to this feeling,

79
00:29:18,631 --> 00:29:22,886
to enter an alliance with these very few

80
00:29:23,470 --> 00:29:27,849
in the encounter
with the visage of the sun.

81
00:30:02,967 --> 00:30:03,009
.

82
00:30:45,093 --> 00:30:45,802
.

83
00:30:46,427 --> 00:30:47,762
Give it to me!

84
00:30:56,104 --> 00:30:57,981
Have you heard about the new ones?

85
00:31:01,818 --> 00:31:03,069
Which new ones?

86
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:07,365
Now some are 
supposed to be also coming here, to us.

87
00:31:08,658 --> 00:31:09,534
Oh, ok.

88
00:31:13,663 --> 00:31:15,456
The clock has stopped.

89
00:31:17,083 --> 00:31:19,836
Oh, I will make it run again then.

90
00:31:20,837 --> 00:31:22,338
How much did that cost?

91
00:31:22,964 --> 00:31:23,798
50.

92
00:31:36,561 --> 00:31:36,603
.

93
00:31:39,480 --> 00:31:41,608
What do you expect from life?

94
00:31:42,859 --> 00:31:44,861
Nothing,I’ll let myself get surprised.

95
00:31:45,403 --> 00:31:47,155
For now I’ll expect something to eat.

96
